1. *Sever* je jako hladan danas. (The *north* is very cold today.)
2. Moramo da idemo *na sever*. (We have to go *north*.)
3. Živim *na severu* grada. (I live in the *north* of the city.)
4. Autobuska stanica se nalazi *severoistočno* odavde. (The bus station is located *northeast* of here.)
5. Naša zemlja se nalazi na *severnoj hemisferi*. (Our country is located in the *northern hemisphere*.)
6. *Severni* vetrovi donose hladnoću. (The *northern* winds bring cold weather.)
7. *Severozapadni* deo zemlje je najrazvijeniji. (The *northwest* part of the country is the most developed.)
8. *Severni pol* je jako hladan i neprijateljski prema ljudima. (The *North Pole* is very cold and inhospitable to humans.)
9. Sveže voće i povrće se najbolje održava na *severnijim* temperaturama. (Fresh fruit and vegetables are best preserved at *cooler* temperatures.)
10. Imamo *severni* ulaz u zgradu. (We have a *northern* entrance to the building.)